quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Chiasikha emikhono chibili chia Abu Lahab, naye mwene nasikha."
  111,2,"Omwandu kukwe shikwamukhoonya tawe nohomba ebiayakhalabanila."
  111,3,"Aliinjila mumulilo kupupuchilanga."
  111,4,"Nende Omukhasi wuwe omuchinji muno wetsikhwi."
  111,5,"Mwikosi mumwe alirebwamwo omukoye kwaborolwa."
